{"tid":2311120,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"其實長期病患老人家點解唔早d死?","createTime":"2020-12-03T22:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T03:49:12.000Z","uid":277186,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fc6b4c5f50d9c1a9088fc4d2ba4b45288600cf6e","tid":2311120,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T22:45:44.000Z","msg":"健康個d都還好，<br />\n<br />\n有d後生唔知點用個身體 老左有長期病患訓係張床等死，連自理能力都無 點解仲要生存? 明天 下個月 下年都係無窮無盡既臥床同睇住自己步入死亡，今日死同訓多幾年後再死有咩分別? <br />\n<br />\n有屋企人照顧都證明你有屋企人錫 中年時期做人都叫正常。有d屋企人睇都唔睇下 擺係老人院 醫院，我覺得佢地唔係可憐 試諗下做人幾失敗先會臨老無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc782b48e91cfdd4be75acbffb9e856a689fa74","tid":2311120,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T22:46:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c30abdc053a55c2f34571f69bcef6428e759edf4","tid":2311120,"uid":283494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T22:56:34.000Z","msg":"樓主注意身體健康"},{"pid":"672a62d425bbae202398a5fb368d6f1d5c537e68","tid":2311120,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffc782b48e91cfdd4be75acbffb9e856a689fa74","tid":2311120,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T22:46:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:10:13.000Z","msg":"我身體健康後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果老左要長期臥床無得救 我肯定會自殺"},{"pid":"2ecf2818a108c687f6e6d59dba0bfac39ac6f655","tid":2311120,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c30abdc053a55c2f34571f69bcef6428e759edf4","tid":2311120,"uid":283494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T22:56:34.000Z","msg":"樓主注意身體健康"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:10:50.000Z","msg":"有做運動 飲食均衡 晚睡早起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b396db9becd6329af1432f4b985fabe977038c","tid":2311120,"uid":260744,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12